    <string name="firstlaunch">
        Hey, glad you found my app! With the last update a lot has happened, so I would like to show you the news here.\n
        \n
        Dragging from the left edge of the screen to the right opens the menu. Here you find the access to the different functions and settings.\n
        \n
        You can switch between 2 and 4 player mode here. There is also a dice function and a counter manager.\n
        The latter is used to keep track of the +/- X tokens on your cards.\n
        \n
        If you have any suggestions or ideas for improvement, you are welcome to contact me by e-mail: feedback@mjurtz.com.\n
        \n
        Thank you!
    </string>

    <string name="intro_1_header">MTG LifeCounter</string>
    <string name="intro_1_description">Hey, thanks for downloading! I\'d like to quickly guide you through the app, which you can skip by clicking the button in the bottom left corner.</string>

    <string name="intro_2_header">Navigation</string>
    <string name="intro_2_description">By sliding from the left hand side of the screen to the right, you can open the menu.</string>

    <string name="intro_3_header">Settings</string>
    <string name="intro_3_description">The settings provide a way to customize several things like colors or default values as you like.</string>

    <string name="intro_4_header">Game</string>
    <string name="intro_4_description">The main view is used to manage games. You can select between 2- and 4-player modes. When closing the app, standings will be saved.</string>

    <string name="lite_intro_4_header">Game</string>
    <string name="lite_intro_4_description">The main view is used to manage games. When closing the app, standings will be saved.</string>

    <string name="intro_5_header">Energy Saving Mode</string>
    <string name="intro_5_description">If your phone has an AMOLED-Display, you can make use of the power-saving mode which darkens most of the main view.</string>

    <string name="intro_6_header">Dice</string>
    <string name="intro_6_description">the dice feature gives you the functionality of a 20-sided dice.</string>

    <string name="intro_7_header">Counter Manager</string>
    <string name="intro_7_description">With the counter management you can keep track of your +1 counters at all times.</string>

    <string name="intro_8_header">About</string>
    <string name="intro_8_description">That\'s it! If you have any feedback, improvement ideas or questions, I would be happy to hear from you. You can find my contact details in the about menu.</string>

